      <title>法国刚刚摆脱衰退，西班牙经济飙升：GDP最新</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/france-just-dodges-recession-with-output-flat-europe-gdp-latest</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国去年下半年勉强摆脱了衰退，而西班牙经济则以 2022 年中期以来最快的速度增长——为欧元区也能避免经济衰退带来希望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-30/france-just-dodges-recession-with-output-flat-europe-gdp-latest</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Jan 2024 06:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
